title: Bloodlust - Helen Harper.epub
description:
Mack is scrambling to wrest back some control over her life, balancing the need to keep her squabbling council in check and locate the necromancer Endor at the same time. Old threats and old alliances keep springing back up to haunt her, and Corrigan, the Lord Alpha of the Brethren, would be perfectly happy if the earth swallowed her up whole and she was never seen again. Unfortunately he may just get his wish...
Genre: Fantasy
